OL,3,CGrieving mother says missed
OL,4,Copportunities led to death of baby
OL,6,FA mother from Swadlincote in
OL,7,FDerbyshire says if she had been able
OL,8,Fto see her GP face to face, her baby
OL,9,Fdaughter might be alive today.
OL,11,FA consultation over the phone with her
OL,12,Fdoctor resulted in a mis-diagnosis.
OL,13,FHayley Johnson lost her baby, Evelyn,
OL,14,F13 hours after she was born at Queens
OL,15,FHospital Burton in August last year.
OL,17,F"I kept getting lower back pain, every
OL,18,Ftime that I called them, it was always
OL,19,Fa telephone appointment. I said I'd
OL,20,Flike to see a GP.
