OL,6,F"They said sorry, we have got no
OL,7,Fappointments available."
OL,9,FShe was told to take codeine and apply
OL,10,Fa tummy support later, a few weeks
OL,11,Flater she was admitted to Queen's
OL,12,FHospital Burton with a ruptured
OL,13,Fplacenta, a loss of blood.
OL,15,FHayley said that during 26 week and 6
OL,16,Fday pregnancy never saw her GP face to
OL,17,Fface, she did see other medical
OL,18,Fprofessionals at Queen Hospital's
OL,19,FBurton.
