OL,3,CGrieving mother says missed
OL,4,Copportunities led to death of baby
OL,6,F15 years ago, her son was born with
OL,7,Fmedical complications.
OL,9,FIt was recommended that during her
OL,10,Fnext pregnancy she receive additional
OL,11,Fsupport from her GP and the hospital.
OL,13,FHayley added: "They called me up for a
OL,14,Fpostnatal check six weeks later, and
OL,15,Fthe doctor asked how I was feeling?
OL,17,F"I said how do you expect me to feel?
OL,18,Fyou never wanted to see me all the way
OL,19,Fthrough the pregnancy so why do you
OL,20,Fwant to see me now?"
