OL,3,CGrieving mother says missed
OL,4,Copportunities led to death of baby
OL,6,FThe case has been taken up by Hayley's
OL,7,Flocal MP who is demanding action and
OL,8,Fimprovements for all expectant mums.
OL,10,FThe Health Secretary Wes Streeting
OL,11,Fsaid that "families deserve truth and
OL,12,Fjustice, there must be accountability
OL,13,Ffor failings, and services must
OL,14,Fimprove.
OL,16,F"I'm committing to doing whatever it
OL,17,Ftakes to provide patients and babies
OL,18,Fwith safe, comfortable and dignified
OL,19,Fcare."
