OL,6,FHayley's GP, Swadlincote surgery said:
OL,7,F"We cannot comment on the
OL,8,Fcircumstances of any patient because
OL,9,Fof patient confidentiality. "Any
OL,10,Fpatient is able to raise a formal
OL,11,Fcomplaint and with their GP practice
OL,12,Fby contacting them directly.
OL,14,F"We welcome the opportunity to
OL,15,Fcontinue to learn how to improve
OL,16,Fmaternity care in Derbyshire."
